9. Styling rules

Global rules
	•	use rounded cards: rounded-2xl
	•	use subtle borders: border border-slate-200
	•	use white card surfaces against a light neutral page background
	•	use shadow-sm only, not heavy shadows
	•	keep spacing tight and purposeful

Typography
	•	page title: text-2xl font-semibold
	•	card title: text-base font-semibold
	•	metadata labels: text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide
	•	body: text-sm text-slate-700

Status styling

Use clear semantic treatments:
	•	success: green tint
	•	warning/partial: amber tint
	•	pending: slate or blue-gray
	•	error: red tint

Avoid multiple bright banners.

